snippet.title: Omni - The Crystal of New Hope
snippet.description:
OMNI is a massively multiplayer online shooter slash loot game (MMOSSL).

Omni!
The crystal brought us a chance to fight. If only we had found it earlier, many could have been saved. Now one of the few crystal shards lays at the heart of New Hope City, creating a sanctuary for our people. 

Omni Webpage: https://www.play-omni.com/ 

Follow us on Discord:
https://discord.gg/Wtf7Vzm
